WEDDING DAY NO-NOs ❌

1. A Big no to face wax for  facial hair removal
( being in this industry for 7-8 years now , I’ve witnessed few brides getting burnt skin moments before their big day )

2. No peeling treatments 
 ( peeling treatments will peel your skin to generate new skin on which makeup can not be done so all these treatments should be stopped at least month before you makeup appointment)

3. No facials atleast 20 days prior to your event

  4. No new Skincare routine 
( experiment with new serums or toner might affect that perfect skin causing unwanted breakouts )

5. Do not compromise your beauty sleep

  6. Waxing / threading 3-4 days prior to the event 
( so your skin is not irritated/red and gets time to heal)

7. Skip alcohol or fried food night before your event to avoid getting bloated and dehydrated face
